<ArticleLayout
  title="Living with Pets"
  description="Practical advice for carpets and sofas when you live with pets: odors, embedded hair and accidents, with professional cleaning options in Greater Montreal."
>
  <p>We love our pets, but they can be hard on carpets and upholstery. Hair, mud, and occasional accidents are part of daily life.</p>

  <h2>Persistent odors</h2>
  <p>Pet urine often penetrates into the carpet backing and underlay. Surface cleaning is usually not enough. Professional treatment uses targeted injection tools and enzymes that break down odor-causing bacteria at the source.</p>

  <h2>Embedded pet hair</h2>
  <p>Pet hair clings tightly to synthetic fibers. A mechanical pre-brush step helps release deeply embedded hair that standard vacuuming often misses.</p>
</ArticleLayout>
